data.value: Begin with all spinners set equal to their labelled value. For each spinner, from minimum to maximum, adjust the output power such that your CALIBRATED EXTERNAL METER is equal to the spinner value. Record the values appearing in the Thetis 'Fwd Pwr' meter. After completing measurements for all spinners, enter your recorded values into the respective spinners. DO NOT USE POWER EXCEEDING THE RATING OF YOUR RADIO!
